{"id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0001", "text": "你叫我這麼感動 但是這是我 你有可能戲弄", "structure": {"line_index": 1, "char_count": 18}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 4, 5, 5, 3, 9, 2, 2, 2, 5, 2, 5, 5, 5, 9, 0, 4, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["nei5", "giu3", "ngo5", "ze5", "mo1", "gam2", "dung6", "daan6", "si6", "ze5", "si6", "ngo5", "nei5", "jau5", "ho2", "nang4", "hei3", "lung6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "叫", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這麼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "感動", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "但是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "可能", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "戲弄", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "夢到內河", "artists": ["張國榮"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1093", "prev_line_id": null, "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0002", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0002", "text": "怎麼肯親手展示 如何被抱擁 我兩手還有用", "structure": {"line_index": 2, "char_count": 18}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [9, 3, 9, 3, 9, 9, 2, 0, 0, 2, 5, 9, 5, 5, 9, 0, 5, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["zam2", "mo1", "hang2", "can1", "sau2", "zin2", "si6", "jyu4", "ho4", "bei6", "pou5", "jung2", "ngo5", "loeng5", "sau2", "waan4", "jau5", "jung6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "怎麼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "肯", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "親手", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "展示", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "如何", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "被", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "抱", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "擁", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "兩手", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "還有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "用", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "夢到內河", "artists": ["張國榮"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1093", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0001", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0003", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0003", "text": "你贈我一巴掌吧 爲什麼未痛 我也許在發夢", "structure": {"line_index": 3, "char_count": 18}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 2, 5, 3, 3, 9, 2, 2, 3, 2, 4, 5, 5, 9, 2, 4, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["nei5", "zang6", "ngo5", "jat1", "baa1", "zoeng2", "baa6", "sam6", "mo1", "mei6", "tung3", "ngo5", "jaa5", "heoi2", "zoi6", "faat3", "mung6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "贈", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一巴掌", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "吧", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "爲什麼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "未痛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也許", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "在", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "發夢", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "夢到內河", "artists": ["張國榮"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1093", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0002", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0004", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0004", "text": "當初的溫馨舉動 拿來做分手的慶功 令我筋竭力窮", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 21}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 3, 3, 3, 9, 2, 0, 0, 2, 3, 9, 3, 4, 3, 2, 5, 3, 4, 2, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["co1", "dik1", "wan1", "hing1", "geoi2", "dung6", "naa4", "loi4", "zou6", "fan1", "sau2", "dik1", "hing3", "gung1", "ling6", "ngo5", "gan1", "kit3", "lik6", "kung4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "當初", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "溫馨", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "舉動", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "拿來", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "做", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "分手", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "慶功", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "令", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "筋", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "竭力", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "窮", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "夢到內河", "artists": ["張國榮"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1093", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0005", "text": "自那日遺下我 我早化做磷火 湖泊上伴你這天鵝", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 20}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 5, 2, 0, 2, 5, 5, 9, 4, 2, 0, 9, 0, 2, 2, 5, 5, 3, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["zi6", "naa5", "jat6", "wai4", "haa6", "ngo5", "ngo5", "zou2", "faa3", "zou6", "leon4", "fo2", "wu4", "bok6", "bun6", "nei5", "ze5", "tin1", "ngo4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "自", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "那日", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "遺下", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "早", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "化做", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "磷火", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "湖泊", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "上伴", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "天鵝", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "夢到內河", "artists": ["張國榮"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1093", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0006", "text": "但你爲何還要 也許單手 怕扼不死我", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 5, 0, 0, 4, 5, 9, 3, 9, 4, 3, 3, 9, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["daan6", "nei5", "ho4", "waan4", "jiu3", "jaa5", "heoi2", "daan1", "sau2", "paa3", "ak1", "bat1", "sei2", "ngo5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "但", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "爲何", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "還要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也許", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "單手", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "怕", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "扼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "死", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "夢到內河", "artists": ["張國榮"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1093", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0007", "text": "若要死 這一刻正是 愉快 高峯 請給我更多", "structure": {"line_index": 7, "char_count": 17}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 4, 9, 5, 3, 3, 4, 2, 0, 4, 3, 3, 9, 3, 5, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["joek6", "jiu3", "sei2", "ze5", "jat1", "hak1", "zing3", "si6", "jyu4", "faai3", "gou1", "fung1", "cing2", "kap1", "ngo5", "do1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "若", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "要死", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一刻", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "正是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愉快", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "高峯", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "請", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "給", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "更", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "多", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "夢到內河", "artists": ["張國榮"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1093", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0006", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0008", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0008", "text": "在內河上 我在內河上", "structure": {"line_index": 8, "char_count": 9}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 2, 0, 5, 2, 2, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["zoi6", "noi6", "ho4", "ngo5", "zoi6", "noi6", "ho4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "在", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "內河", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "上", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "在", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "內河", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "上", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "夢到內河", "artists": ["張國榮"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1093", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0007", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0009", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0009", "text": "望着沿岸高潮 快救活我 溫暖我十秒 快將我怨念傳召", "structure": {"line_index": 9, "char_count": 22}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 2, 0, 2, 3, 0, 4, 4, 2, 5, 3, 5, 5, 2, 5, 4, 3, 5, 4, 2, 0, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["mong6", "zoek6", "jyun4", "ngon6", "gou1", "ciu4", "faai3", "gau3", "wut6", "ngo5", "wan1", "nyun5", "ngo5", "sap6", "miu5", "faai3", "zoeng1", "ngo5", "jyun3", "nim6", "cyun4", "ziu6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "望", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "着", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沿岸", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "高潮", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "快", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "救活", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "溫暖", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "十秒", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "快", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "將", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "怨念", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "傳召", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "夢到內河", "artists": ["張國榮"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1093", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0008", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0010", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0010", "text": "誰還在內河上 猶如做夢那樣 但奈何沒有天橋", "structure": {"line_index": 10, "char_count": 19}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 2, 2, 0, 0, 0, 2, 2, 5, 2, 2, 2, 0, 2, 5, 3, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["seoi4", "waan4", "zoi6", "noi6", "ho4", "jau4", "jyu4", "zou6", "mung6", "naa5", "joeng6", "daan6", "noi6", "ho4", "mut6", "jau5", "tin1", "kiu4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "誰", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "還", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "在", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "內河", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "上", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "猶如", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "做夢", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "那樣", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "但", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "奈何", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "天橋", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "夢到內河", "artists": ["張國榮"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1093", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0009", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0011", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0011", "text": "跨不過這雙臂膀 會將你壯麗忘掉 如果有這需要", "structure": {"line_index": 11, "char_count": 20}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [4, 3, 4, 5, 3, 4, 9, 3, 5, 4, 2, 0, 2, 0, 9, 5, 5, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["kwaa3", "bat1", "gwo3", "ze5", "soeng1", "bei3", "bong2", "zoeng1", "nei5", "zong3", "lai6", "mong4", "diu6", "jyu4", "gwo2", "jau5", "ze5", "seoi1", "jiu3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "跨", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不過", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "雙", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "臂膀", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "會", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "將", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "壯麗", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "忘掉", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "如果", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "需要", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "夢到內河", "artists": ["張國榮"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1093", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0010", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0012", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0012", "text": "差不多不懂感動 就像死掉了 兩腳竟能震動", "structure": {"line_index": 12, "char_count": 18}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 3, 3, 3, 9, 9, 2, 2, 2, 9, 2, 5, 5, 4, 9, 0, 4, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["caa1", "bat1", "do1", "bat1", "dung2", "gam2", "dung6", "zau6", "zoeng6", "sei2", "diu6", "liu5", "loeng5", "goek3", "ging2", "nang4", "zan3", "dung6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "差不多", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "懂", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "感動", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "就", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "像", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "死", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "掉", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "了", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "兩腳", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "竟能", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "震動", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "夢到內河", "artists": ["張國榮"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1093", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0011", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0013", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0013", "text": "不應該這麼激動 仍然能夠哭 我眼睛還有用", "structure": {"line_index": 13, "char_count": 18}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 3, 5, 3, 3, 2, 0, 0, 0, 4, 3, 5, 5, 3, 0, 5, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["bat1", "goi1", "ze5", "mo1", "gik1", "dung6", "jing4", "jin4", "nang4", "gau3", "huk1", "ngo5", "ngaan5", "zing1", "waan4", "jau5", "jung6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "應該", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這麼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "激動", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "仍然", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "能夠", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "哭", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "眼睛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "還有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "用", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "夢到內河", "artists": ["張國榮"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1093", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0012", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0014", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0014", "text": "咬住我這雙手吧 但願這陣痛 說我不是發夢", "structure": {"line_index": 14, "char_count": 18}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 2, 5, 5, 3, 9, 2, 2, 2, 5, 2, 4, 4, 5, 3, 2, 4, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ngaau5", "zyu6", "ngo5", "ze5", "soeng1", "sau2", "baa6", "daan6", "jyun6", "ze5", "zan6", "tung3", "syut3", "ngo5", "bat1", "si6", "faat3", "mung6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "咬住", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "雙手", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "吧", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "但願", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "陣痛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "說", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "發夢", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "夢到內河", "artists": ["張國榮"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1093", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0013", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0015", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0015", "text": "你爲何這麼衝動 拿流浪的軀體抱擁 直到筋竭力窮", "structure": {"line_index": 15, "char_count": 21}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 0, 5, 3, 3, 2, 0, 0, 2, 3, 3, 9, 5, 9, 2, 4, 3, 4, 2, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["nei5", "ho4", "ze5", "mo1", "cung1", "dung6", "naa4", "lau4", "long6", "dik1", "keoi1", "tai2", "pou5", "jung2", "zik6", "dou3", "gan1", "kit3", "lik6", "kung4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "爲何", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這麼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "衝動", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "拿", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "流浪", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "軀體", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "抱擁", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "直到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "筋", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "竭力", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "窮", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "夢到內河", "artists": ["張國榮"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1093", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0014", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0016", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0016", "text": "自那日遺下我 我早化做磷火 湖泊上伴你這天鵝", "structure": {"line_index": 16, "char_count": 20}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 5, 2, 0, 2, 5, 5, 9, 4, 2, 0, 9, 0, 2, 2, 5, 5, 3, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["zi6", "naa5", "jat6", "wai4", "haa6", "ngo5", "ngo5", "zou2", "faa3", "zou6", "leon4", "fo2", "wu4", "bok6", "bun6", "nei5", "ze5", "tin1", "ngo4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "自", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "那日", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "遺下", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "早", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "化做", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "磷火", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "湖泊", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "上伴", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "天鵝", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "夢到內河", "artists": ["張國榮"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1093", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0015", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0017", "paragraph_id": "para_05"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0017", "text": "但你爲何還要 也許單手 怕扼不死我", "structure": {"line_index": 17, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 5, 0, 0, 4, 5, 9, 3, 9, 4, 3, 3, 9, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["daan6", "nei5", "ho4", "waan4", "jiu3", "jaa5", "heoi2", "daan1", "sau2", "paa3", "ak1", "bat1", "sei2", "ngo5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "但", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "爲何", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "還要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也許", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "單手", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "怕", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "扼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "死", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "夢到內河", "artists": ["張國榮"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1093", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0016", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0018", "paragraph_id": "para_05"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0018", "text": "若要死 這一刻正是 愉快 高峯 請給我更多", "structure": {"line_index": 18, "char_count": 17}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 4, 9, 5, 3, 3, 4, 2, 0, 4, 3, 3, 9, 3, 5, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["joek6", "jiu3", "sei2", "ze5", "jat1", "hak1", "zing3", "si6", "jyu4", "faai3", "gou1", "fung1", "cing2", "kap1", "ngo5", "do1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "若", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "要死", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一刻", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "正是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愉快", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "高峯", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "請", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "給", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "更", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "多", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "夢到內河", "artists": ["張國榮"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1093", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0017", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0019", "paragraph_id": "para_05"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0019", "text": "(誰還)在內河上 我在內河上", "structure": {"line_index": 19, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 2, 2, 0, 5, 2, 2, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["seoi4", "waan4", "zoi6", "noi6", "ho4", "ngo5", "zoi6", "noi6", "ho4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "(", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "誰", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "還", "pos": "X"}, {"text": ")", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "在", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "內河", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "上", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "在", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "內河", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "上", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "夢到內河", "artists": ["張國榮"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1093", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0018", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0020", "paragraph_id": "para_06"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0020", "text": "望着沿岸高潮 快救活我 溫暖我十秒 快將我怨念傳召", "structure": {"line_index": 20, "char_count": 22}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 2, 0, 2, 3, 0, 4, 4, 2, 5, 3, 5, 5, 2, 5, 4, 3, 5, 4, 2, 0, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["mong6", "zoek6", "jyun4", "ngon6", "gou1", "ciu4", "faai3", "gau3", "wut6", "ngo5", "wan1", "nyun5", "ngo5", "sap6", "miu5", "faai3", "zoeng1", "ngo5", "jyun3", "nim6", "cyun4", "ziu6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "望", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "着", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沿岸", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "高潮", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "快", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "救活", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "溫暖", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "十秒", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "快", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "將", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "怨念", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "傳召", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "夢到內河", "artists": ["張國榮"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1093", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0019", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0021", "paragraph_id": "para_06"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0021", "text": "誰還在內河上 猶如做夢那樣 但奈何沒有天橋", "structure": {"line_index": 21, "char_count": 19}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 2, 2, 0, 0, 0, 2, 2, 5, 2, 2, 2, 0, 2, 5, 3, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["seoi4", "waan4", "zoi6", "noi6", "ho4", "jau4", "jyu4", "zou6", "mung6", "naa5", "joeng6", "daan6", "noi6", "ho4", "mut6", "jau5", "tin1", "kiu4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "誰", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "還", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "在", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "內河", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "上", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "猶如", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "做夢", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "那樣", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "但", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "奈何", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "天橋", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "夢到內河", "artists": ["張國榮"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1093", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0020", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0022", "paragraph_id": "para_06"}}
